Class TestingConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jLOAF.performance.TestingConfig

  • public class TestingConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    this class is a testing configuration class, it is used to test the performance of different agents with different parameters, such as different similarities and different reasoners.
